Recipe To Riches Canada - Season 3, Episode 4




Appetizers

In this episode of Recipe to Riches, a mom from Gibsons, BC with Italian roots, a dairy worker and dad from Newmarket, ON and a food-blogging mom with Indian roots now in Markham, ON compete to find out whose appetizer will be on grocery store shelves across the country this weekend.




Original Air Date: 19-Mar-2014
